{"tid":2487312,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"郭榮鏗正式發聲明移居加拿大 退出公民黨","createTime":"2021-04-13T12:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T12:29:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":61,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"981f652f80a8ed8e5fd25c944b43b3bdea12401e","tid":2487312,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/874p0/0x0/100/none/b0e81897c8547b6e31c7b9969852b248/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210413/_2021041320334819464.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F874p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2Fb0e81897c8547b6e31c7b9969852b248%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210413%2F_2021041320334819464.jpg&h=05e00b7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年11月被禠奪立法會議員資格後退出政壇的郭榮鏗，與家人先後離開香港，前往加拿大定居，他日前透露正尋求取回加拿大公民身分。他晚上發表聲明，稱已正式向公民黨提出退黨申請，又表示為公民黨帶來的不便致歉。<br />\n<br />\n聲明全文如下：<br />\n<br />\n「感謝連日來各方友好的關心與慰問。<br />\n<br />\n本人郭榮鏗已正式向公民黨提出退黨申請。<br />\n<br />\n本人衷心感謝公民黨 － 特別是余若薇女士、梁家傑先生及吳靄儀女士 － 過去一直以來給予的栽培、機會、支持與包容，讓我有機會服務香港市民，以及捍衛香港的核心價值；並藉此機會，就本人若然曾經為公民黨帶來的不便等致歉。<br />\n<br />\n最後，祝願公民黨仝人平安。<br />\n<br />\n2021年4月13日」"},{"pid":"158b86f866e9d1756b68012fffdc7d687a7d3153","tid":2487312,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:43:09.000Z","msg":"方向報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b22e5891a466955789f1c90c7404ca9aa991e541","tid":2487312,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:43:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713e8bc006397fa97d9f3e3b929f4affcc6a8bd8","tid":2487312,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"158b86f866e9d1756b68012fffdc7d687a7d3153","tid":2487312,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-